# BRSR Regulatory Compliance Tracker

Automated tool to extract, analyse, and score Business Responsibility and Sustainability Reports (BRSR) for compliance.  
It generates TXT, CSV, and database outputs that can be used for analytics or dashboards (e.g., Power BI).

